Mu rwego rwo kubungabunga ibidukikije no guharanira imirire myiza, Umuryango AEE watanze ibiti 2,080 bya avoka byo gutera muri [[Akarere ka Huye|Huye]] na [[Akarere ka Nyaruguru|Nyaruguru]], biba bikeya kuko byifuzwaga na benshi.


Umuryango AEE wabitanze ku baturage bo mu Murenge wa Mukura mu [[Akarere ka Huye|Karere ka Huye]], no mu Murenge wa Ngera ndetse n’uwa Ngoma mu [[Akarere ka Nyaruguru|Karere ka Nyaruguru]]. Byahawe abaturage bakeya batoranyijwe n’inzego z’ubuyobozi. Abatuye muri Mukura no muri Ngera bagiye bahabwa igiti kimwe buri wese, naho muri Ngoma bo bahabwa ibiti bitatu buri wese.<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/ubuhinzi/ubuhinzi/article/hatanzwe-ibiti-bya-avoka-byo-gutera-biba-nk-agatonyanga-mu-nyanja</ref>
